---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';

// Puedes definir tus habilidades y experiencia aquí
const skills = [
  { name: "HTML/CSS", level: 90 },
  { name: "JavaScript", level: 85 },
  { name: "React", level: 80 },
  { name: "Node.js", level: 75 },
  { name: "Astro", level: 70 },
  { name: "Git", level: 85 }
];

const experiences = [
  {
    title: "Desarrollador Frontend",
    company: "Empresa A",
    period: "2022 - Presente",
    description: "Desarrollo de interfaces de usuario con React, implementación de APIs, etc."
  },
  {
    title: "Desarrollador Web",
    company: "Empresa B",
    period: "2020 - 2022",
    description: "Creación de sitios web responsivos, mantenimiento de aplicaciones existentes."
  }
];
---

<MainLayout title="Sobre Mí | Mi Portfolio">
  <section class="about-section">
    <h1>Sobre Mí</h1>
    
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="lead">
          ¡Hola! Soy Diego, un desarrollador apasionado por crear experiencias web increíbles.
        </p>
        
        <p>
          Me especializo en el desarrollo frontend con un enfoque en crear interfaces de usuario intuitivas
          y atractivas. También tengo experiencia en desarrollo backend y me encanta aprender nuevas tecnologías.
        </p>
        
        <p>
          Cuando no estoy programando, disfruto de la fotografía, senderismo y leer libros de ciencia ficción.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="about-image">
        <img src="/images/profile.jpg" alt="Diego" />
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="skills-section">
      <h2>Mis Habilidades</h2>
      
      <div class="skills-container">
        {skills.map(skill => (
          <div class="skill">
            <div class="skill-info">
              <span class="skill-name">{skill.name}</span>
              <span class="skill-percentage">{skill.level}%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="skill-bar">
              <div class="skill-progress" style={`width: ${skill.level}%`}></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="experience-section">
      <h2>Experiencia</h2>
      
      <div class="timeline">
        {experiences.map(exp => (
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h3>{exp.title}</h3>
              <div class="timeline-meta">
                <span>{exp.company}</span>
                <span>{exp.period}</span>
              </div>
              <p>{exp.description}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .about-section {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-content {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 3rem;
  }

  .about-text {
    flex: 2;
  }

  .about-image {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .about-image img {
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .skills-section, .experience-section {
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .skills-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .skill-info {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .skill-bar {
    height: 10px;
    background-color: #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 5px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .skill-progress {
    height: 100%;
    background-color: #3490dc;
    border-radius: 5px;
  }

  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background-color: #e2e8f0;
  }

  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .timeline-dot {
    position: absolute;
    left: -2.1rem;
    top: 0.25rem;
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: #3490dc;
    border: 3px solid white;
  }

  .timeline-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    color: #6b7280;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-content {
      flex-direction: column-reverse;
    }

    .about-image {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-image img {
      max-width: 300px;
    }

    .skills-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>